headline: National Veterinary Associates Welcomes Brian McKeon to Board of Directors
summary: National Veterinary Associates (NVA) is pleased to announce the appointment of Brian McKeon to its Board of Directors. McKeon brings a wealth of expertise in finance and strategic planning, having held leadership roles at multiple publicly traded corporations.
